headline: Stryker (NYSE:SYK) Declares US$0.84 Dividend Per Share; 5% Annual Increase
summary: Stryker (NYSE:SYK) recently affirmed its commitment to shareholder value by declaring a quarterly dividend of $0.84 per share, maintaining consistency with its focus on strong dividend growth. Over the last month, Stryker's shares appreciated 11% amid broader market gains following the announcement of a U.S.-U.K. trade deal, which lifted investor sentiment. headline: Stryker declares an $0.84 per share quarterly dividend
summary: Portage, Michigan, May 08, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Stryker (NYSE:SYK) announced that its Board of Directors has declared a quarterly dividend of $0.84 per share payable July 31, 2025, to shareholders of record at the close of business on June 30, 2025, representing an increase of 5.0% versus the prior year and unchanged from the previous quarter.
